%% NetScript docs diagram: aspire-resource-graph
%% The .NET Aspire AppHost orchestrates a NetScript app's process graph in local dev.
%% Theme-neutral; hand-authored SVG sibling lives at assets/diagrams/aspire-resource-graph.svg
flowchart TB
  AppHost["Aspire AppHost\n(declares & starts resource graph)"]
  Dashboard["Aspire Dashboard\n(telemetry / logs / traces)"]

  subgraph Resources["Resource graph"]
    Postgres[("Postgres\nresource")]

    subgraph Orders["orders plugin"]
      API["HTTP API service"]
      Worker["worker\n(background processor)"]
      Saga["saga-runner\n(background processor)"]
    end
  end

  AppHost -->|starts| Postgres
  AppHost -->|starts| API
  AppHost -->|starts| Worker
  AppHost -->|starts| Saga

  Postgres -->|connection string / service discovery| API
  Postgres -->|connection string / service discovery| Worker
  Postgres -->|connection string / service discovery| Saga

  Dashboard -.observes.- Postgres
  Dashboard -.observes.- API
  Dashboard -.observes.- Worker
  Dashboard -.observes.- Saga
